        " امْشِ بَيْنَ يَدَيِ الْجَنَازَةِ وَ خَلْفَهَا ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Humeyd Bin Ziyad, from Al Hassan Bin Muhammad Al Kindy, from someone else, from Aban Bin Usman, from Muhammad Bin Muslim, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Ja’far<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘Walk in front of the coffin and behind it’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "5. Humayd ibn Ziyad has narrated from al-Hassan ibn Muhammad al-Kindiy from more than one person from Aban ibn ‘Uthman from Muhammad ibn Muslim who has said the following: “Abu Ja‘far, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said, ‘(In a funeral procession) walk in front or behind (the coffin).”’ "
        ]
      }
